parameters:
If we get any closer, it seems like we won't be
able to avoid a fight.
Do you want to proceed to the system?

Sakura: Alright, this time it's finally the last
battle.

Rurika: Yes, let's proceed without letting our
guard down.

Sakura & Rurika: In order for our master to
dominate the city \I[15], In order for our husband
to dominate the city \I[15]

Kenichi (After this battle is over, the city
will... ugh)

Sakura: Phew, as expected of the central system of
the city.

Rurika: They were tough opponents, but with this,
we can make the city belong to our husband, right?

Kenichi (If things continue like this... I won't
be able to protect the peace of the city)
Kenichi (I am a Future Special Police...)
Kenichi (I can't allow such a thing!!)
Do you want to stop SYSTEM Sakura and Rurika?

Sakura: I've reevaluated you a bit, even though
you're a masochistic small-dicked \I[15].

Rurika: Well, should I say you have no sense of
your place, or should I call you reckless?

Rurika: It seems like it's been a while since you
needed some punishment \I[15].
The difference in ability is clear.
Kenichi: I will stop you, Onee-chan!
Congratulations on reaching the SYSTEM IF end.

I will rewind time before the final boss battle of
SYSTEM and resume the game.

Rurika: Conquering the city, it's the final touch
\I[15].

Sakura: It's an important system that protects the
city \I[15].

Sakura: Kenichi, make sure to deliver the
finishing blow \I[15].

Rurika: I can never defy my husband again \I[15],
and not only that, I can't defy Onee-chan and the
others either \I[15].

Sakura: If you understand it well, then you can do
it, right? \I[15]
We were able to restore peace to the city.

The Future Special Police... The newly revived
Pink Snake Gang... From the front, from the back,
they are still protecting the peace of the city.
However... it's for the sake of Kimohiko.
